        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Liang Zhen",
          "email": "liang@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2012-06-28 01:52:51.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-1577 lnet: should export lnet_net2ni",
        "message": "LU-1577 lnet: should export lnet_net2ni\n\nWe don't want to export lnet_net2ni_locked because it requires\nan extra parameter CPT number, which is internal to LNet and\nconfusing to user, also, no LND is using it/should use it, however,\nLND does need lnet_net2ni() which is an inline function and it is\nreferring lnet_net2ni_locked(), which means it forces us to export\nlnet_net2ni_locked.\nThe way to fix should be simple, we can just dis-inline lnet_net2ni()\nand export itself instead of exporting lnet_net2ni_locked.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I251d42d47770211ae6238ee56972fb9aacd63599\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
